thread.title: SANDER
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by SANDER

author: SANDER
title: SANDER
text: This was my second time to rent a car from Redspot. Everything was exactly as smooth as the first time and the car was equally clean and decent as well. When it comes to quality, Redspot is no different from other popular rental companies. However, based on my experience, their price levels beat all others.
